item.title: Near Me Messaging Demo Videos
item.description: Near Me Walkthrough # In this video, one of our Natural Language Processing Engineers will walk through the entire process of creating and fine-tuning a Near Me Virtual Agent. Set Up Your Agent # In this video, we show the process of setting up your first virtual agent with Near Me Messaging! Observe Your Agent # In this video, we look through the different ways to observe your Near Me Virtual Agent’s performance.
